## Variables
set $mod Mod4
set $left h
set $down j
set $up k
set $right l

set $TERMINAL footclient
set $TERMEXPLORER yazi
set $READER zathura
set $EXPLORER nemo
set $VIDEO mpv
set $IMAGE imv
set $BROWSER firefox
set $MENU albert show

## Config
